    </div>

    <ul id="pagination-technical" class="pagination-sm"></ul>
    <div id="page1" class="page">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xl-9 col-lg-8">
                <div class="card shadow mb-4">
                    <!-- Card Header -->
                    <div class="card-header py-3 d-flex flex-row align-lis-center justify-content-between">
                        <h4 class="m-0 m-0 font-weight-normal text-secondary">Maintenance</h4>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Card Body -->
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p>
                            <strong>Maintenance</strong> means the degree to which an application is understood, repaired, or
                            enhanced.
                        </p>
                        <ul>
                            <li> (a)(b) How long is the system expected to be used for ? </li>
                            <li> (b) In ten years time, how difficult would it be for a developer to fix bugs in the
                                system? </li>
                            <li> (a)(b) Are the operating system and runtime environment expect to change? </li>
                            <ul>
                                <li>(b) If so, what would be required from maintainers of this system?</li>
                            </ul>
                            <li>
                                (a)(b) Can the correctness of the system be affected by other systems ?
                            </li>
                            <ul>
                                <li>
                                    (a)(b) Can this system affect the correctness of others ?
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

